snippet.title: GOROGOA | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to PC and iOS. http://gorogoa.com

Steam: http://bit.ly/GorogoaSteam
GOG: http://bit.ly/GorogoaGOG
App Store: http://apple.co/iOSGorogoa

Designed, developed, and illustrated by Jason Roberts, Gorogoa is a beautifully hand-drawn story suspended inside a puzzle with a completely unique mechanic. 

Developed by JASON ROBERTS. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2017
